The '''Blagwahr''' were a primitive race from [[Arorua]]. When [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan Kenobi]] and [[Qui-Gon Jinn/Legends|Qui-Gon Jinn]] trained on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]], they saved [[Mosko Bolpa]] from a Blagwahr snare trap. A sacrificial altar was built for a [[Silan]] on a [[Mountain/Legends|mountain]] and it is possible that the Blagwahr people built it.

